STEP-BY-STEP Plan (start as a FEMALE CHARACTER)

Out of the gate, choose Melee sigil, get as high of HP/Def for further questing.

1st Goal: Complete King's Ransom for Piety when moving to world 36
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*Get 13 dragon bones for 43 Prayer*

Complete 'Misthalin Mystery' https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Misthalin_Mystery
        -Level 22 Crafing
				
Complete 'Black Knight's Fortress' https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Black_Knights%27_Fortress

Complete 'Recruitement Drive' https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Recruitment_Drive
        -Level 27 Agility
        -Level 27 Prayer
        -Level 27 Herblore
        -Access to Initiate Armour (Sallet free) 20K for full set
        -Change spawn location
	
Complete 'The Knight's Sword' https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/The_Knight%27s_Sword
	-Needs 15 Smithing, 15 Cooking, 15 Mining
	-Level 52 Smithing

Complete 'Jungle Potion' https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Jungle_Potion
	-Level 32 Herblore

Complete 'Shilo Village' https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Shilo_Village
	-Level 41 Crafting
	
Complete 'Murder Mystery' https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Murder_Mystery
	-Level 44 Crafting
	
Complete 'One Small Favour' https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/One_Small_Favour
	-Needs 36 Agility if I don't have it
	-200K in XP lamps in over 30.
	
Complete 'Holy Grail' https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Holy_Grail
	-Level 59 Prayer
	-Level 70 Def or so
	
Complete 'King's Ransom' https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/King%27s_Ransom
	-Needs 45 Magic
        

        
